Class JsonNullAwareDeserializer

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public final class JsonNullAwareDeserializer
extends JsonNodeDeserializer
    Custom deserializer for JsonNode

    Up to, and including, versions 2.1.4, Jackson's JsonNodeDeserializer deserializes a JSON null value as null. This custom deserializer deserializes it as a NullNode instead.

    See also here.
